e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"飲水中水毒點解要飲8杯水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc58312754fc53ab6332af7ec08d5777a4b4c25","tid":820371,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"但煎蛋真係好正，唔知係咪卵子基因互引，食左會扯晒旗"},{"pid":"3390ea72128fe4db9efd0d56cb24327ac23c9a4a","tid":820371,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6492d9e7007460ff9b8b7ea320679111a6398997","tid":820371,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"071867be8b75669aa512e788f5e0d6857b660f4a","tid":820371,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fcbbfedf30651da899f6a6034fefd8f2e4156e32","tid":820371,"uid":27885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"走黃囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"但有另一個說法話蛋黃先最有營養喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"兩者好似冇衡突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"有衝突，蛋黃有人話係好膽固醇嚟，所以食多多都唔怕"},{"pid":"3c437153c5302913c18f799705117b32fe6e86b7","tid":820371,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"（轉自高登）<br />\n<br />\n仲講雞蛋膽固醇已經錯晒啦 <br />\n其實人體只有7X至80%膽固醇係從食物吸收 <br />\n大部份都係肝製造出嚟 <br />\n而且食物嘅膽固醇亦都唔係全部壞，係有好膽固醇 <br />\n正常食用，真正從食物吸收嘅壞膽固醇其實唔多 <br />\n<br />\n除非你係食人魔，係咁食內臟，或者你身體有異常，否則正常食蛋唔會有大問題 <br />\n有D人天生膽固醇水平較低，更應該日日食去補充膽固醇水平添 <br />\n<br />\n牛奶就真係無咩益，主要係現代工廠式製造問題 <br />\n另外市面好多果汁飲品（非純果汁）其實都加太多糖，都係無益<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6810120&amp;page=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6810120%26page%3D3&d=fa3kQePns4jzxFjcx4JstHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e12203de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6810120&amp;page=3</a>"}]}